items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [eza-ls (⭐1)](https://github.com/birdhackor/zsh-eza-ls-plugin) - Adds aliases allowing [eza (⭐16k)](https://github.com/eza-community/eza), to act as a drop-in replacement for `ls` and `tree`.
*   [terminal-aliases (⭐10)](https://github.com/dvir-levy/terminal-aliases) - Adds convenience aliases for `terraform`, `git` and more.

### Completions / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [bosh (thomasmitchell) (⭐9)](https://github.com/thomasmitchell/bosh-complete) - Tab completion for [BOSH (⭐2.1k)](https://github.com/cloudfoundry/bosh).

### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [gorchak (⭐0)](https://github.com/evgenygorchakov/oh-my-zsh-gorchak-theme/) - Inspired by [robbyrussell (⭐180k)](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes#robbyrussell) and [af-magic (⭐180k)](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes#af-magic). Includes decorators for `git` information and Node.js version.
*   [modern (⭐0)](https://github.com/BadRat-in/zsh-modern-theme) - Automatically adapts to light and dark terminal themes. This theme provides a clean and informative prompt with git integration, command execution time, and a beautiful rainbow directory path.
*   [moonbloom (⭐5)](https://github.com/moonbloom-theme/zsh) - Adapts to the color scheme of your terminal emulator. Includes decorators for current directory and `git` status.

items.title: Awesome Agi Cocosci
items.content_text:
### Abduction / Explanation

*   [Abductive Cognition: The Epistemological and Eco-Cognitive Dimensions of Hypothetical Reasoning](https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007%2F978-3-642-03631-6) - ***Springer***, 2009. \[[All Versions](https://scholar.google.com/scholar?cluster=8707351442527595188)]. Most philosophers of science in the twentieth century have concluded that no logic of creative processes exists and, moreover, that a rational model of discovery is impossible. In short, scientific creative inferences are irrational and there is no “reasoning” to hypotheses. On the other hand, some research in the area of artificial intelligence has shown that methods for discovery could be found that are computationally adequate for rediscovering --- or discovering for the first time --- empirical or theoretical laws and theorems.

items.title: Awesome Sitecore
items.content_text:
### Headless

*   [Angular JSS starter kit for XM Cloud (⭐269)](https://github.com/Sitecore/jss/tree/release/22.0.0/packages/create-sitecore-jss/src/templates/angular-xmcloud) - Sitecore JSS Angular Starter Kit App for XM Cloud.

### XM Cloud

*   [Node XM Cloud Proxy (⭐269)](https://github.com/Sitecore/jss/tree/release/22.0.0/packages/create-sitecore-jss/src/templates/node-xmcloud-proxy) - Node proxy application enables backend functionality and features equivalent to those in our Next.js starter kit for XM Cloud. Was introduced to support the new Angular starter kit. This proxy is designed to work with all SPA frameworks and can also be used to run React and Vue applications, laying the groundwork for future JSS starter kits built for other front-end JavaScript frameworks.
items.content_html:

XM Cloud

  • Node XM Cloud Proxy (⭐269) - Node proxy application enables backend functionality and features equivalent to those in our Next.js starter kit for XM Cloud. Was introduced to support the new Angular starter kit. This proxy is designed to work with all SPA frameworks and can also be used to run React and Vue applications, laying the groundwork for future JSS starter kits built for other front-end JavaScript frameworks.

items.title: Awesome Osint
items.content_text:
### Email Search / Email Check / GitHub

*   [LeakCheck](https://leakcheck.io/) - Data Breach Search Engine with 7.5B+ entries collected from more than 3000 databases. Search by e-mail, username, keyword, password or corporate domain name.
*   [LeakRadar](https://leakradar.io/) - Scans for compromised emails and domains in stealer logs, offering proactive breach prevention and real-time alerts.
